{"tid":1217733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】文翠珊：修例不應違反中英聯合聲明　英國有責任發聲","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T14:01:12.000Z","uid":50457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3db3e24c4d90827dfffad45d14775c6165283e2c","tid":1217733,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"星期三反送中集會演變成大規模衝突，英國首相文翠珊首度回應表示，非常關注《逃犯條例》修訂，認為相關法案，不應違反中英聯合聲明。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊表示，英國有責任為前殖民地的自由發聲，特別是香港有大量英國公民，新修訂的移交安排，要符合中英聯合聲明中，對香港人自由權利的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n英國外相侯俊偉發表聲明，關注特區政府修訂《逃犯條例》，呼籲各界冷靜，促請港府暫停備受爭議的措施，保障香港自由和權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%96%87%E7%BF%A0%E7%8F%8A-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%89%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E7%258F%258A-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%2F&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=b171d064\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E7%258F%258A-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%2F&h=0eb8d5ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%96%87%E7%BF%A0%E7%8F%8A-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%89%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"2cd774a048e61efab0555381c537e5a7516740dd","tid":1217733,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"中國：歷史文件"},{"pid":"a9ecf3872dc4faa6eb5867dced5ac44606509bbd","tid":1217733,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}